column5: Got out for a few hours, turned out to be a great day.  Here's some pics from today...                 Tight Lines,  Vick
Definatley not big fish, but tastey all the same. WTG Vick!
very nice,congrats on a good day
nice fish  that second one looks like a drop back
Nice Lookin shakers,....definately a good sign,..I hope u put a couple back for me to catch....
A good outing, nice healthy looking fish...
WAY TO GO! nice fish. i hope you released some as those micros are the future of our fishery...
thanks for all the positive comments guys, i like the difference in boards.
Yup, definatley not a good idea to post dead fish pics on the other board, no one here cares unless its a musky.
none of those pics have a fish dead in them, the first one was right before we gutted it though.
